Setting up to run the project:

1. Install ruby1.9.1
    1. installing rubygems1.9.1
        - It could still be an old version
            - install rubygem updater
                - $ sudo gem install rubygems-update
            - run the updater $ sudo update rubygems
                - Will show all the improvements that have been made...
        - Install gems
    2. Gems to install:
    - sudo gem install mysql
    - json ~> 1.7.7
    - nokogiri
    - github_api

2. Install MySQL
    1. Need to be able to make an account that has full privileges to the database I create.